{"tid":1338552,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第時如果我有女 一定要改名叫如水","createTime":"2019-07-21T13:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T13:55:59.000Z","uid":233118,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1914481b21d85c0d3e006764b4903b3a03dcf184","tid":1338552,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:47:51.000Z","msg":"今日大家做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咗咁多日，練習咗咁多嗰星期<br />\n大家終於知道be water 嘅重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n變身後見到現場成班狗企定定喺防線<br />\n眼神充滿憤怒，但係又十分無奈兼疲累<br />\n重點喺返到屋企啲狗仲要企成晩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老婆又要守空閨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n治愈到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果第時有女，一定改名叫如水以記念今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868a8725fd386ca783f3f5dc01f361f58422d90c","tid":1338552,"uid":15854,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"陳如水🤔<br />\n英文文：水魚 陳🤔"},{"pid":"6864d5b38512caf3aea4400db3a5dcffaddbbd31","tid":1338552,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:49:30.000Z","msg":"btw 元朗朋友小心牛屎佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遇襲要反擊<br />\n牛屎佬唔喺冇牌爛仔<br />\n唔驚襲警<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535f9ed39ba550346bc5904c40339d569545e9dd","tid":1338552,"uid":86221,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"熊若水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58ade81ad7bc209a4e1beae1141a51c673edff4","tid":1338552,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"868a8725fd386ca783f3f5dc01f361f58422d90c","tid":1338552,"uid":15854,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"陳如水🤔<br />\n英文文：水